net.sf.mmm.util.query.api.path

Interface PathFactory

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BooleanPath, CollectionPath<V,E>, ComparablePath<V>, EntityAlias<E>, EntityBeanPath<V>, ListPath<E>, MapPath<K,V>, NumberPath<V>, Path<V>, PathRoot<E>, SetPath<E>, StringPath
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPathFactory, AbstractPathRoot, Alias, BooleanPathImpl, CollectionPathImpl, ComparablePathImpl, EntityBeanPathImpl, ListPathImpl, MapPathImpl, NumberPathImpl, PathImpl, SetPathImpl, StringPathImpl

    public interface PathFactory
    This is the abstract interface for a factory to create instances of Path and its sub-types. An instance of PathFactory is either a Path itself or a PathRoot.
    Since:
    8.0.0
    Author:
    hohwille
